<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= appName %></title>
    <link href="/public/css/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="font-sans antialiased text-gray-800 from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 min-h-screen">

    <header class="bg-white shadow-md py-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-indigo-700"><%= appName %></h1>
            <nav class="space-x-6">
                <a href="/" class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-200">Home</a>
                <a href="/admin/service/list" class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-200">Ver Serviços</a>
                <a href="/web/login" class="text-lg font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 transition duration-200 px-4 py-2 border border-indigo-600 rounded-md">Login Admin</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 mt-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-2xl">
        <section class="text-center mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-4">
                <%= welcomeMessage %>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Simplifique seu dia. Encontre e agende os melhores serviços com apenas alguns cliques.
            </p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="action-card bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-inner text-center mb-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-4">Pronto para Agendar?</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-indigo-800 mb-6">Utilize o link abaixo para visualizar todos os serviços disponíveis e iniciar seu agendamento.</p>
            <a href="/web/service" class="inline-block bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white text-xl font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 ease-in-out">
                Ver e Agendar Serviços &rarr;
            </a>
        </section>
        
        <section class="admin-links bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Área Administrativa</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">Gerencie sua plataforma, usuários e serviços. Acesse o painel ou a documentação da API.</p>
            <div class="space-x-6">
                <a href="/web/login" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
                    Acessar Painel
                </a>
                <a href="/docs" class="inline-block text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 font-semibold px-6 py-3 border border-indigo-600 rounded-lg transition duration-300">
                    Documentação (Swagger)
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="text-center mt-12 py-6 text-gray-500 text-sm">
        <p>&copy; 2024 <%= appName %>. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>